    "D. Dataset Statistics and DistributionThe database contains 3,345 reviews obtained through multiple e-commerce sites.",
    "Table I shows the review distribution statistics by source.TABLE I: Data Collection Sources Platform Total Reviews Daraz 2,431 Facebook 467 Rokomari 273 Shajgoj 82 Other 92 Table II provides the distribution of extracted triplets across different sentiment polarities.TABLE II: Aspect-Opinion-Sentiment Triplet Distribution Aspect Category Total Positive Negative Battery Life 732 412 320 Camera Quality 598 301 297 Service 491 278 213 Pricing 824 502 322 Packaging 321 189 132 E. Key Features of the DatasetThe database marks its first category of annotated Bangla ASTE which focuses on product review evaluation.",
